<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <%- include('head') %>
  <title><%= locals.title %></title>
  <meta name="description" content="<%= locals.description %>" />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="<%= locals.title %>" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="<%= locals.description %>" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://oldschoolgames.eu/privacy-policy" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="OldSchoolGames" />
</head>

<body class="layout">
  <%- include('navbar') %> <%- include('left-sidebar') %>
  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <%- include('flash') %>
      <section>
        <h1 class="text-lg" style="margin-bottom: 5px">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p style="
              color: rgb(var(--muted-rgb));
              font-size: 0.9em;
              margin-bottom: 25px;
            ">
          Last updated: March 2026
        </p>

        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px">
          This Privacy Policy describes how
          <strong>OldSchoolGames.eu</strong> ("we", "us", "our") collects,
          uses, and protects your personal data when you use this website. We
          are committed to protecting your privacy and complying with the
          General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and applicable EU/Czech
          data protection law.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin: 25px 0 10px">
          1. Data Controller
        </h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px">
          The data controller responsible for this website is:<br />
          <strong>RobLib</strong><br />
          Czech Republic<br />
          Email:
          <a class="color-primary underline" href="mailto:contact@oldschoolgames.eu">contact@oldschoolgames.eu</a>
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin: 25px 0 10px">
          2. What Data We Collect
        </h2>

        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600">a) Comments</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px">
          Anyone can post a comment without creating an account. When you post
          a comment, we store the comment text, an optional display name
          (nickname) you provide, and a timestamp. If no nickname is given, the
          comment is posted as <em>anonymous</em>. Comments are publicly
          visible.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600">
          b) Usage data (Google Analytics)
        </h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px">
          We use <strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> to understand how
          visitors use the site. This service collects anonymized information
          including pages visited, time spent on pages, device type, and
          approximate geographic location (country/region level). IP addresses
          are anonymized. Google Analytics sets cookies in your browser. For
          more information, see
          <a class="color-primary underline" href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600">
          c) Browser-local storage (favorites & recently played)
        </h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px">
          Your favorite games and recently played games are stored in your
          browser's
          <strong>localStorage</strong>. This data never leaves your device
          and we have no access to it.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin: 25px 0 10px">
          3. Legal Basis for Processing
        </h2>
        <ul style="padding-left: 20px; line-height: 2; margin-bottom: 15px">
          <li>
            <strong>Comments:</strong> Legitimate interest (enabling community
            interaction; no account or personal data required)
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Legitimate interest (improving
            and understanding usage of the site)
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin: 25px 0 10px">4. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px">
          We do not sell or rent your personal data. We share anonymized usage
          data with Google via Google Analytics. No other third parties
          receive your personal data.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin: 25px 0 10px">5. Data Retention</h2>
        <ul style="padding-left: 20px; line-height: 2; margin-bottom: 15px">
          <li>
            <strong>Comments:</strong> Retained until an administrator removes
            them. Because comments are posted without an account, we have no
            way to link them to you after submission — if you need a comment
            removed, please contact us.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Retained for 14 months per
            Google's default settings.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin: 25px 0 10px">
          6. Your Rights (GDPR)
        </h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px">
          Under GDPR, you have the following rights:
        </p>
        <ul style="padding-left: 20px; line-height: 2; margin-bottom: 15px">
          <li>
            <strong>Right of access</strong> — request a copy of your personal
            data
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Right to rectification</strong> — request correction of
            inaccurate data
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Right to erasure</strong> — request deletion of your
            personal data ("right to be forgotten")
          </li>
          <li><strong>Right to restrict processing</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Right to data portability</strong></li>
          <li>
            <strong>Right to object</strong> to processing based on legitimate
            interest
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px">
          To exercise any of these rights, contact us at
          <a class="color-primary underline" href="mailto:contact@oldschoolgames.eu">contact@oldschoolgames.eu</a>. We will respond within 30 days.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin: 25px 0 10px">7. Security</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px">
          All data is transmitted over HTTPS. We take reasonable technical and
          organisational measures to protect your data against unauthorised
          access.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin: 25px 0 10px">
          8. Changes to This Policy
        </h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "last
          updated" date at the top of this page will reflect any changes.
          Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of
          the revised policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-md" style="margin: 25px 0 10px">9. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For any privacy-related questions or requests, email us at
          <a class="color-primary underline" href="mailto:contact@oldschoolgames.eu">contact@oldschoolgames.eu</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <%- include('right-sidebar') %> <%- include('footer') %>
</body>

</html>
